fields.question: How do I book a tutor?
fields.answer: To book a tutor, navigate to the 'Booking' section, select a tutor, and choose an available time slot.

fields.question: What is the cancellation policy?
fields.answer: You can cancel a booking up to 24 hours before the scheduled time without any charges.

fields.question: How do I reset my password?
fields.answer: To reset your password, click on the 'Forgot Password' link on the login page and follow the instructions.

fields.question: How can I contact customer support?
fields.answer: You can contact customer support via email at support@example.com or by calling (123) 456-7890.

fields.question: What payment methods are accepted?
fields.answer: We accept all major credit cards, PayPal, and Apple Pay.

fields.question: How do I create an account?
fields.answer: To create an account, click on the 'Sign Up' button on the top right corner of the homepage and fill in the required information.

fields.question: Can I change my booking?
fields.answer: Yes, you can change your booking up to 24 hours before the scheduled time. Please contact customer support for assistance.

fields.question: Do you offer group tutoring sessions?
fields.answer: Yes, we offer group tutoring sessions. You can find more information in the 'Group Sessions' section.

fields.question: How do I leave a review for a tutor?
fields.answer: After your session, you will receive an email with a link to leave a review for your tutor.

fields.question: What subjects do you offer tutoring in?
fields.answer: We offer tutoring in a wide range of subjects including math, science, languages, and more. Check the 'Subjects' section for a full list.
